title: Cachumba
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Indian, Beer/Wine, Pan-Asian, African, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Several menu items suitable for vegans. Specialty is the rice table where wait staff brings a variety of dishes from different countries of origin for you to sample along with rice. This can be 100% vegan (advertised on the menu) and a wide range of dishes are provided. Relaxed, informal atmosphere and staff and restaurant owner show good knowledge of vegan requirements.
